{"word":"χοανεύω","slug":"χοανεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χοανεύω</b></el> <el>(χοᾰνεύω,) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to cast into a mould</i> (<el>χοάνος</el>), <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to cast</i> metal:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>κεχωνευμένος</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>χοά˘νη</el>\n"}]}